snippet.title: Space Raiders Official Game Trailer 2017
snippet.description:
Download it for free:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.kiril.main.game

Space Raiders is a 2017 2D science fiction space-shooter video game, developed by Kiril Raykov and published for Android devices. The game is also scheduled for a release on Windows. Developed on Java using LibGDX framework.

Business inquiries:
kirilraykov@gmail.com

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100001123770027
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/kirilraykov/

Game Trailer by Ivaylo Todorov.
